creator: eiji-gravion@hotmail.com
text:
I've heard that there are issues with internet explorer causing I/O errors when keep-alive is enabled with https however I'm getting these I/O errors for ALL browsers and with ALL users no matter what when keep-alive is enabled browsing https pages.

Disabling keep-alive will make the errors at the end of the log go away...
